hopobject.body: How many would you like? buy generic viagra online australia Between the ages of 16 and 24, when he was still under the spell of Chopin, Scriabin composed numerous tiny Preludes. He eventually gathered 24 of them together to form a set. The debt to Chopin is obvious in the pedal-hazed dreaminess, and the way the music vacillates between minor-key melancholy and major-key warmth. But the opening phrase has a pure floating quality, almost free of expression, which is very Scriabin. It’s played here by Yuja Wang.
